142
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:48,830
Natáčaniu?

143
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,920
S kým?

144
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,400
So mnou?

145
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,600
