150
00:08:03,090 --> 00:08:05,070
Čo by mohlo byť horšie než oblečenie?

151
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:07,140
Tieto veci, ktoré sa tu živo vrtia.

152
00:08:07,140 --> 00:08:11,200
Najviac neznášam psy, mačky a zajace!

153
00:08:13,610 --> 00:08:15,060
Ah! Prečo vrieskaš?

154
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:17,520
Veď ja som ich sem nepriniesla.

155
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,890
Kde je Go Dong?

156
00:08:19,890 --> 00:08:22,520
Povedz Go Dongovi, aby sa ich úplne zbavil!

157
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,880
