371
00:21:54,130 --> 00:21:55,820
Neboj sa.

372
00:21:57,720 --> 00:22:01,640
Ak ma podoprieš zo spodu, myslím,
že dokážem vyliezť hore.

373
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,840
Čo?

374
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:04,840
Ja? Ty?

375
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:09,350
Zbláznila si sa?

376
00:22:09,350 --> 00:22:11,480
Ah! Štylistka Jang!

377
00:22:12,670 --> 00:22:14,240
Pozriem sa, či už odtiaľto vyleziem!

378
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:16,780
