397
00:24:11,910 --> 00:24:13,340
Huh?

398
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:15,750
Ako to mám urobiť?

399
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:25,390
Podrž ju na chvíľu.

400
00:24:26,050 --> 00:24:27,330
Zbláznila si sa?

401
00:24:27,330 --> 00:24:30,990
Potom čo? Chceš, aby som
liezla dnu spolu s ňou?

402
00:24:40,990 --> 00:24:42,790
Vlož ju dnu.

403
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:48,400
Zostaň tu na chvíľu. Prepáč.

404
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:55,580
